it, that I don't even know what it was thinking, you

36:32.596 --> 36:39.184
see. I know this sounds silly, but I think it was 
that way.

36:49.462 --> 37:02.978
I think he saw in his own mind so far down the road of 
history here, and he did things today that fit that

36:49.462 --> 37:02.978
pattern a hundred years from now in his mind.

37:07.379 --> 37:22.426
Now, I'm not sure how you do this, because I've 
never tried to make my daily actions conform to

37:07.379 --> 37:22.426
something that I think will be or ought to be 50 or 
100 years from now. So I'm not sure whether it takes

37:22.446 --> 37:27.014
a brilliant mind or not, but I would certainly 
think it does. And I believe that's what he did. And

37:30.440 --> 37:32.323
I think he did a damn good job of it.

37:40.336 --> 37:58.304
He always did or seemed to try to do the very best for 
the United States in the problem at hand, meaning

37:40.336 --> 37:58.304
its immediate effect. Whether he was trying to do 
the best for it in the long range, I have some very

37:58.324 --> 38:04.453
serious questions in my mind.

38:08.129 --> 38:18.459
because I think what he had in mind was a society, an 
objective in mind was a society that does not now

38:08.129 --> 38:18.459
exist. Neither ours, nor the communist, nor 
socialism, or anything else.

38:31.031 --> 38:34.795
And it was never possible for me to get a clear 
enough picture of what that society was in his mind

38:35.028 --> 38:45.681
to frame it into something I could see.

38:50.206 --> 38:59.297
But that feeling was always there after a year's 
association with him, for example.

39:02.467 --> 39:06.491
and he was very genuine and very sincere about 
everything.

39:09.374 --> 39:31.377
Yet,

39:09.374 --> 39:31.377
in that way of mind, there seemed to be a, an

39:09.374 --> 39:31.377
area, naive area that either things just weren't 
important to him, or that he had no thought

39:32.858 --> 39:46.758
experience about, that he just let shine,

39:32.858 --> 39:46.758
didn't make any difference.

