40:10.272 --> 40:16.741
And yet he never did see that it was stupid, or he 
certainly never did acknowledge it. So why the

40:18.684 --> 40:20.667
hell did he do it, you see? If I take that little 
problem, it didn't turn out to be so damn little,

40:21.649 --> 40:27.537
but relatively and translate it up here to these 
bigger things, it looks still the same way, you

40:28.225 --> 40:32.971
see. How come he thinks just this way? Because he 
doesn't tell you, no more than he defended why he

40:35.814 --> 40:41.221
did it then.

40:44.705 --> 40:46.928
So, I really never did know. I don't know right now, 
just exactly what to think. As a physicist, he was

40:52.134 --> 40:55.498
certainly a brilliant man, no question about 
that.

