do it and have the Russians do it and hold it over our

41:33.181 --> 41:42.493
head. He just must have known that. He never said 
that, but he must have. So, why did he take that

41:46.759 --> 41:48.722
position? Is it because he feared retribution by 
God? I don't believe so. I don't believe he

41:55.123 --> 41:56.404
believed any of that.

